summary:
Areas of Clinical Skill

At the St. Antonius-Hospital in Gronau I have gained extensive experience in all basic urological and investigative treatment methods. Moreover I developed a special interest in robot-assisted urological surgery and acquired competence in this field. I have performed robot- assisted procedures, like prostatectomies, port placements and fascia closures. Furthermore, I have performed many endoscopic procedures, general urological surgery in pediatric urology and uro-gynecology.
